member.name: P:SpawnProcess.My.Resources.Resources.HelpText
member.summary:
Looks up a localized string similar to SpawnProcess.exe -path "C:\Path\To\Process.exe" -args "-arg1 goesHere -arg2 goesHere" -windowstyle hidden|normal|minimized|maximized -workingdirectory "C:\Path\To"
-args and -windowstyle and -workingdirectory are optional.
